 the name well, was malden) who was obviously a shared account or someone with 0 life cause by everything I could tell and others he was sitting in EC about 18-20 hours a day.  SA would farm everything there was to farm and take it to him to sell.  They literally controlled every mob there was in the high end game.  Nothing was taken without them being involved somehow.  I played on lanys for about a year before moving here because a RL friend kept bugging me to change, i was getting fed up with EQ and wasnt sure if it was the server or the game that I was fed up with so I gave Brell a try.  It was different at first, I didnt really even like it at first to tell the truth.  See on Lanys because the end game was so unplayable for the extreme majority people would get to the high 40's get sick of the BS and make an alt.  Literally there was this huge community of sub 40's that had been playing the game since beta but never moved to the high end game so they all worked very well together and welcomed n00bs like me in warmly.  On Brell the low end game is a bit different, a large portion of it is high end players alts who typically expect anyone they group with (for the few that either have to or even choose to group) to know the game and their character in and out before lvl 10 so it was a little harsh for me for a while because even though I knew my bard from playing one on lanys (moveing chars wasnt an option then of course so I started fresh) I was by far no expert.  Anyway got through that crap and got to the near high end game and found this board.  Ive been visiting the board for many months I just dont post often to answer Twiggies question in another thread about me being a newcomer.  I didnt know what to expect from the high end game here, I never got there on Lanys just saw all the crap SA did and such but when I found hte board, imagine what I thought when I saw reservations for the planes, for dragons even?  OMG it was beautiful, for atleast a decent part of the first stage of the end game there was no uber guild dictating how the game would be played, how loot would be distributed, and who could kill what mob.  I have seen how bad FCFS can be, and seeing that I can never imagine believing FCFS could be good.  All the equations of guilds doing mob x then moving on is great in theory, and maybe even would work here, but it didnt work on Lanys when I was there because one guild wouldnt allow it.  This is why I vote reserveable, this is why I believe Trak will be farmed, because I have seen it happen.<br><br>Reako<br>55 Bard<br>Dracaena Arcanum <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#464446><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uhikaruichijyo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hikaru Ichijyo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>AI OBOETE IMASU KA?</span><br>  Posts: 933<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/20/02 10:56:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisfrm71.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=61.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.cox.net/cgoebel5/sig/ico_Hiksnickers.jpg Width=100 Height=174></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Yeah</span><hr size=1> Ow that chunk of text is one incredible eyesore. Space things out plz kthx!~<br><br>Oh and incidentally...heh heh heh heh...in your mind those damn ubers are all the same no matter what server they're on. Don't worry, the ones on this server ARE out to get you....AND YOUR LITTLE DOG TOOOOOOO!!!! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><DIV ALIGN="center"><IMG SRC="http://members.cox.net/cgoebel5/sig/Hiksig7.jpg" BORDER="0"><BR><FONT FACE="Tahoma" SIZE="3"><B>Hikaru Ichijyo</B></FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Tahoma, Arial" SIZE="2">- - - <B>56th Level Outrider</B> - - - <BR>- - - <A HREF="http://pub22.ezboard.com/bsent